options.text: I need another assignment.
Have you any rewards for me, or anything to trade?
Let's talk about the difficulty of my assignments.
What can you do apart from Slayer Master stuff?
Er... Nothing...

ef14b85a-acb0-4628-aa28-366948dee82e.title: Krystilia
ef14b85a-acb0-4628-aa28-366948dee82e.text:
You're still meant to be slaying <slayer_task_type>(s),
you have <slayer_task_remaining> to go.

f4777043-7b09-42ca-a800-d569a46e9813.title: <player>
f4777043-7b09-42ca-a800-d569a46e9813.text: Have you any rewards for me, or anything to trade?

b31a524e-7d62-4173-8097-428d218a259c.title: Krystilia
b31a524e-7d62-4173-8097-428d218a259c.text:
I have quite a few rewards you can earn, and a wide
variety of Slayer equipment for sale.

options.text: Look at rewards.
Look at shop.
Cancel.

21a398e3-1290-45d1-abdf-9d7065f01867.title: <player>
21a398e3-1290-45d1-abdf-9d7065f01867.text: Let's talk about the difficulty of my assignments.

8a99a459-69e4-4359-bdf1-5038d7a0bcd4.title: Krystilia
8a99a459-69e4-4359-bdf1-5038d7a0bcd4.text:
Other Slayer Masters take your combat level into
account when choosing tasks for you, so they won't set
you anything to hard. But I don't do that - if you get
a task from me, it could be anything from which you
have the Slayer level, provided you can physically get to
it.

5bb154cb-f66e-4826-a169-baeea3239c79.title: <player>
5bb154cb-f66e-4826-a169-baeea3239c79.text: What can you do apart from Slayer Master stuff?

0d1a4b5e-c94f-4e1e-b13c-6ece1e4afd10.title: Krystilia
0d1a4b5e-c94f-4e1e-b13c-6ece1e4afd10.text:
Quite a lot! Those stupid guards thing they've trapped
me here for causing trouble, but I can get back out to
the Wilderness for some fun anytime I like.

1f13da42-0dac-45fd-b051-5c0adcfb242a.title: Krystilia
1f13da42-0dac-45fd-b051-5c0adcfb242a.text:
Hey, perhaps you'd like me to fix it so that you
respawn in Edgeville whenever you die. If you love the
Wilderness as much as I do, you might enjoy that.

options.text: Tell me more.
That doesn't interest me.

1cebb9ab-10cb-4d64-aab2-92c768b354d6.title: Krystilia
1cebb9ab-10cb-4d64-aab2-92c768b354d6.text: Maybe you just can't handle Edgeville!

e31c9e00-c8f7-4374-99f2-95a47f5d4370.title: Krystilia
e31c9e00-c8f7-4374-99f2-95a47f5d4370.text:
Alright, here's the deal: Whenever you drop dead, I'll
try to make you reappear in Edgeville, down by the
southern ruins. You'll lose your items as normal.

94bd2dc6-1bc7-425a-94d9-8ce3e5428c6a.title: Krystilia
94bd2dc6-1bc7-425a-94d9-8ce3e5428c6a.text:
My magic won't affect you if you die in some fancy
place like Castle Wars or the Duel Arena; those places
have their own magic trying to make you 'safe'.

9fb2086f-ea12-4c5b-ab99-4334c8574aeb.title: Krystilia
9fb2086f-ea12-4c5b-ab99-4334c8574aeb.text:
I'll want a one-off payment of 5 million coins. If you
get your respawn changed later, and then need me to
set it back to Edgeville, I won't bill you again.

4160a682-804c-4ccf-a94b-07ed750c08ff.title: <player>
4160a682-804c-4ccf-a94b-07ed750c08ff.text: I'm not carrying that much money.

options.text: Okay, switch my respawn to Edgeville.
I'm not interested

a8907e59-96a7-4a8d-a997-354a98341c39.title: Krystilia
a8907e59-96a7-4a8d-a997-354a98341c39.text:
Hah, Fine, you can keep respawning elsewhere, and I
hope you enjoy it.

9c27fad2-6dbb-43f1-813a-0562c240b84c.title: <player>
9c27fad2-6dbb-43f1-813a-0562c240b84c.text: Okay, switch my spawn to Edgeville.

2368cdeb-c700-441d-9b59-7da31af92b07.title: Krystilia
2368cdeb-c700-441d-9b59-7da31af92b07.text: So do you want to respawn in Edgeville in future?

options.text: Please switch my respawn back to Edgeville.
No, I don't want to respawn in Edgeville.

7658a513-b696-44a0-ae00-992ac1d01253.title: <player>
7658a513-b696-44a0-ae00-992ac1d01253.text: No, I don't want to respawn in Edgeville.

70c1b344-a4af-4b52-8382-55fcb5d2de25.title: <player>
70c1b344-a4af-4b52-8382-55fcb5d2de25.text: Please switch my respawn back to Edgeville.

5e0bd7cc-43d3-4786-b847-15165fe8703a.title: Krystilia
5e0bd7cc-43d3-4786-b847-15165fe8703a.text:
Sounds like you're looking for some fun! Are you sure
you can handle it?

options.text: Yes, switch my respawn to Edgeville.
No, maybe another time.

fbb3fc1b-c230-4c48-b273-8cd8cbb1be67.title: <player>
fbb3fc1b-c230-4c48-b273-8cd8cbb1be67.text: Yes, switch my respawn to Edgeville.

66ac3815-8e63-42ff-a1ad-ca504a5ff3bd.title: Krystilia
66ac3815-8e63-42ff-a1ad-ca504a5ff3bd.text: So how's that Edgeville respawn working for you?

options.text: Please switch my respawn back to Lumbridge.
It's fine, thanks.

1eb3f6cf-401e-4d80-af62-53aaad94fe25.title: Krystilia
1eb3f6cf-401e-4d80-af62-53aaad94fe25.text:
You really want to respawn in that dead-end slum?
Are you sure? Come and see me if you want to respawn in
Edgeville again; I won't ask for more money.

53180813-870c-47a7-90d1-c4dd89adf630.title: <player>
53180813-870c-47a7-90d1-c4dd89adf630.text: Please switch my respawn back to Lumbridge.

options.text: Yes, switch my respawn to Lumbridge.
No, I'll keep the Edgeville respawn.

7ca56670-eee2-43bc-b996-6e2db5c44a87.title: <player>
7ca56670-eee2-43bc-b996-6e2db5c44a87.text: No, I'll keep the Edgeville respawn.

076c54a3-9a03-4f6c-99c6-a2862491bb4b.title: <player>
076c54a3-9a03-4f6c-99c6-a2862491bb4b.text: Yes, switch my respawn to Lumbridge.
